title: Ali performs "Blue Lotus" and more Live on KEXP

author: KEXP
description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents Ali performing live in the KEXP studio. Recorded March 19, 2025.

Songs:
Pulse 00:45
Al Janoub 03:54
Orient 07:09
Blue Lotus 09:36
Downtown Strut 14:51

John Paul Patton - Drums

Ayla - Percussion
